# Internal Security Audit Report

## Company
Botium Toys

## Audit Framework
NIST Cybersecurity Framework

## Scope
Review security controls, compliance requirements, and potential risks affecting company infrastructure and customer data.

## Summary
The audit identified multiple gaps in administrative and technical controls that could expose the company to data breaches and regulatory penalties.

Immediate action is recommended to improve identity access management, encryption practices, monitoring capabilities, and business continuity planning.
